WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:02.550
Transformer, 2017: add sinusoidal absolute position before projection.

00:02.550 --> 00:05.850
Shaw et al., 2018: add a learned relative-position representation to the key.

00:05.850 --> 00:09.150
Transformer-XL, 2019: decompose content and relative-position score terms.

00:09.150 --> 00:12.450
T5, TUPE, and DeBERTa: retain, simplify, or disentangle selected additive interactions.

00:12.450 --> 00:15.750
RoFormer Equation 11: state the desired dependence on m minus n before choosing an operator.

00:15.750 --> 00:20.033
RoFormer Equations 12 through 16: absolute rotations collapse to one relative rotation.
